The paper proposes a novel multilinear dynamical system for tensor time series analysis, which involves machine learning and signal processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as they are also related to machine learning and signal processing. Additionally, the paper involves statistical analysis and modeling, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.ST (Statistics) and cs.IT (Information Theory) sub-categories.
